extends layout

block content
  h1 Second Step, Sumbit your signature of the following Message with your active key:
  h4.text-info.lead #{challenge}
  h3.
     in this step, just sign the message above with your active key of the bts account 
     your provide(#{account}), and submit the signature. How to get your active key ?
     check any bts ui and check "account" - "permissions",
     then under active key permissions tag, click the public key and then show WIF.
     How to sign? you may check 
     #[a(href='https://pluswave.github.io/WifSign/') here ] .
  form(method='post', action='/BtsAuth/verifyAccount')
    input.form-control(name='sign', type='text')
    input(type='hidden', name='account' value='#{account}')
    input(type='hidden', name='challenge' value='#{challenge}')
    button.btn.btn-primary submit
